name: Multicolor One Shoulder Dress
description:
I wore this beautiful dress to a birthday dinner for one of my close friends. The theme was Manhattan chic so I added a studded belt and a cropped leather vest but the dress can definitely stand alone!!! This dress is colorful and it compliments any shape! One layer of tulle is underneath an a-line skirt but you can definitely add a petticoat to fluff it up even more!

Size Small. 

Belt and Vest not included.

Email for additional pics.

name: Bebe Sequin Jumpsuit
description:
I purchased this beautiful one of a kind jumpsuit from Bebe for New Years Eve 2012 and it was a HIT! It has pockets and it has a stretchy lining underneath to fit all of your curves perfectly! It has a zipper closure in the back and it stops right above the ankle. I enjoyed this jumpsuit and I hate to part ways with it buuuuttt I know I probably won't EVER wear it again. Therefore, I need someone to take over ownership of it and treat it with the utmost respect! lol 

Size X-small.

Sold out company wide!
Original Price $169
